{
  "stem": "2581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No one thought that he's going to die the next day, except those that threw themselves at the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But this-- being in Birkenau was so fast, you know, that before we knew, we were taken on the railroad cars and we were sent to a division of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were sent to Kaufering where there were-- Kaufering was a division of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- there were 11 camps over there from Lager number einz, camp number-- number one, and camp 11.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived at four-- camp number four, which was six kilometers from the city of Landsberg am Lech.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the city where Hitler wrote-- was imprisoned and wrote It's also the city where we lived after the war, before we came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in that camp, they started to organize groups to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, we cleaned up the camp and we prepared it for people, you know, other arrivals.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were the first ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had-- and then we started to go-- to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We worked [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the fields.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We worked laying cable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if it was electric cable-- probably telephone cables.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a town nearby, Lechfeld, which is also very close-- it's on-- it's between Landsberg and Augsberg, where we laid the cables.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It had to be telephone cables.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in between that, there were-- were woods where, after a while when people started to die, this is where they were very buried, in those woods between Lechfeld and Lands-- and Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the camp, it didn't take very long.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
